{{Template shortcut|bgg publisher}}

This template displays an external link to a page for a game publisher at the [[BoardGameGeek]] website.

== Usage ==
Unnamed parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>|<var>NAME</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>|<var>NAME</var>|<var>ID2</var>|<var>NAME2</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>|<var>NAME</var>|<var>ID2</var>|<var>NAME2</var>|<var>ID3</var>|<var>NAME3</var>}}

Named parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}<var>ID</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}<var>ID</var>|name{{=}}<var>NAME</var>}}

== Example ==
''Usage in the article {{tsl|en|Columbia Games||Columbia Games}}, with article name as link text:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|49}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}49}}

''Usage with name parameter as link text:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|49|Columbia Games}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}49|name{{=}}Columbia Games}}

''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|49|Columbia Games}}
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id=49|name=Columbia Games}}

''URLs:''
: <kbd>[https://www.boardgamegeek.com/company/49 https://www.boardgamegeek.com/company/{{hilite|49}}]</kbd> (used in template)
: <kbd>[https://www.boardgamegeek.com/boardgamepublisher/49/columbia-games https://www.boardgamegeek.com/boardgamepublisher/{{hilite|49}}/columbia-games]</kbd> (redirect at website)

